Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又无视顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:09.17,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Buster Machine·soixante-six
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:09.17,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}【soixante-six】\N法语数字66
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优等生的时代结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要击落它们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转得分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要逆转了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上！上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被击中了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再差一点就能领先了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到了 琪可的求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪可 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出局的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的成绩就不可动摇了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的胜负似乎已经见分晓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和优等生没得比呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs56}Topless的力量是为了渴望和平的每个人而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs56}对于太阳系防卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年的冻京宣誓仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年得分最高的Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在宇宙军的理事总会 担任自治互助会的总代表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是照着现成的稿子念罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样 诺诺似乎也办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是最高得分者的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想办法修好我的Buster Machine啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,soixante-six是不可能重建的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上只有31架Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以它可珍贵着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想成为第一名嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs56}我们在此宣誓 将善用Topless的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs56}为全人类带来幸福和繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺也宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs56}这次大规模的Topless集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺真是孩子气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs56}推测可能是为了对付一直以来造成问题的“木星急行”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体人员注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰将比预定晚15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达伽利略太空站 欧罗巴国际宇宙港
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当地的时间为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就是木星？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.57,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,851)}太阳系 第5行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:00.54,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\fsp\frz270\fscy130\fn@FZHuaLi-M14\fsp5\pos(1051,705)}最讨厌Topless了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着由我来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是在宇宙军的协助下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集结了近半数现役Buster Machine所进行的大作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙怪兽大军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是木星急行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正以周期90天的椭圆轨道逐渐接近木星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳系的大动脉“大圆航线”每次也不得不因此而停航
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:22.17,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}【大圆航线】（orthodrome）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:22.17,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)\pos(72,82)}通过两点间大圆的劣弧；在航海或航空中，运用此特性而走最短距离的航线称为大圆航线。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人们似乎无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么现在才要处理？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都已经放任十几年不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来似乎有什么隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 没看到最先提议的那对双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他们在泰坦度假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰坦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要到那种乡下地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs56}我们为双胞胎跑腿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs56}听说沼气浴对皮肤很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 要不要出去观光一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的话 回去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了 优等生发言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进行这次的作战还少一架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被你们家那位和果子系搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家太严苛了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和睦些嘛
