Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道建造中的新型机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会要他们提早完成装备组装 参加这次的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台Buster Machine已经苏醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么简单就能苏醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使装备组装完成 有一半还是无法苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾听说过它会被销毁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让诺诺驾驶新的Buster Machine吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感动！太感动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又离诺诺莉莉的梦想更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只笨鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶当然是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下就可以赢拉尔克了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台是隔了数十年才制造的新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.83,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Buster Machine·quatre-vingt-dix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.83,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}【quatre-vingt-dix】
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.83,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\pos(83,77)}法语数字90
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是还没有战斗经验值的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员的选定基准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说会和现有的Buster Machine不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs56}这表示诺诺也有机会是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的Buster Machine是否会苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟首位驾驶员有很大的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且听说操纵技术也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs56}关于操纵技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs56}我曾被姐姐称赞过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs56\fad(100,200)}哼 哼 自满中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是说还没决定是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你不能驾驶Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.34,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,861)}木星 南特拉斯 住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.34,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,847)}同区 -271层1b-3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.55,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,855)}民生局医院 木星分院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.43,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,857)}宇宙放射线病房大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会那么简单就得宇宙放射线病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说什么没诊断书就不能驾驶Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么问题都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,quatre-vingt-dix要由我来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这表示我们是竞争对手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你什么都没搞懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得那个人是在这里转弯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸一点新鲜空气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么古老的宇宙都市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是在人类被关在太阳系之前就已经存在的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真的比月球的冻京还古老吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它本来是为了与宇宙怪兽作战而建造的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如在战场上被击沉或许还比较幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其露出这种丑陋的姿态…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霉味好重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙船时代的通道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在区域规划时被保留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 果然找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是正牌的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的秘密基地 有被大人发现过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定是Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在见习中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些小鬼是哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然耍别人还偷人家东西 胆子实在有够大…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们觉得不这么做的话 你们是不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真是Topless的话 有件事希望你能帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这里下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这座没有天空的宇宙都市下雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得到雪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却降不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是因为太冷而冻住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个白白又亮亮的东西 如果飘了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 让雪飘下来好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想一起堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛 琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Topless的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是能让大家幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有想过Buster Machine的幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦醒了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定会为人类赴死作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它被创造的目的就是如此 所以也是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初你身为dix-neuf的驾驶员那时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想过这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在你还能跟它交谈的话 你想问看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像诺诺这样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能成为quatre-vingt-dix的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对它来说或许就会很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼可拉可不这么想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩很可能是Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是真的这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于最近一直在下沼气雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖掘的进度有点落后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木星急行那边没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然连新型机都被派出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们安排的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这个秘密圈可是受到很多人认同的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰坦蟹好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的晚餐也别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别搀和了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前就先照我们所说的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个机器人女孩如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双胞胎的秘密圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭到宇宙怪兽袭击的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺是Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺可能会被选中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Topless的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是能让大家幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将善用Topless的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为全人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想一起堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆个雪人好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计木星急行将如同以往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掠过南方住宅区的侧边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在各自轨道上的指定地点 发射空间机雷后迅速归航
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,48小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙怪兽面前布下机雷原
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其诱导至北侧的非住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自治互助会将在此布下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你很期待诺诺？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3、2、1 释放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说自己的操纵技术很高吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是作战中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被责骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关闭讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是早点回去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺要回去作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算直接找他谈判吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只笨鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然罕见地说出“绝不会输给你”这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,quatre-vingt-dix是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样只会让自己更丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然真的生诺诺的气…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们宣誓 将善用Topless的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为全人类带来幸福和繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做出无法做到的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木星是不可能下雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Topless真能让人幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Topless能治好生病的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Topless能让犯罪消失吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能制止战争吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Topless能见到死去的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 诺诺才那么努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺她只是想成为宇宙驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后守护大家罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让她是只笨鸟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.95,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(974,849)}北特拉斯城壁（坍缩炉心遗址）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金星达伶基地的四台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.83,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1054,856)}Buster Machine·vingt-deux
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.83,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}【vingt-deux】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.83,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\pos(79,79)}法语数字22
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经封锁了大部分地区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.04,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(955,866)}Buster Machine·soixante
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.04,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}【soixante】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.04,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\pos(73,73)}法语数字60
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离机雷原还有30
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战进入第三阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.55,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,858)}南特拉斯 住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认折返点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认外围点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和果子系迟到了
