Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动防御战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和果子系的不用出手也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要被卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终防线交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法引诱至北侧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往南特拉斯去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地区有医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,quatre-vingt-dix无法出动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在必须用quatre-vingt-dix战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的 它还没苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,quatre-vingt-dix
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你满脑子只想着分数的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不回应孩子们的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样Buster Machine是不会醒来的
