Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想赢拉尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她无法在宣誓仪式上说出那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么Topless会带给大家幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像有很厉害的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的病我也会帮你治好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个月的生日 我们一起来堆雪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像不像大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑着说“不适合我”的他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宇宙放射线病人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明说过要治好他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤了他的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Topless太无力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连那家医院的孩子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于无法相信自己的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Buster Machine是不会借出自己的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想救那些孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想被那个人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方主力突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“和果子系”的 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用Buster X攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量太多了
